{"tid":1670337,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"炒林鄭？英國傳媒指中央擬任命臨時行政長官特首辦未回覆","createTime":"2019-10-23T03:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T16:00:44.000Z","uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"38346dc45940a212ff2e95c75188fbed1bd788d2","tid":1670337,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:18:18.000Z","msg":"大家點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有英國傳媒報道，中國政府擬任命臨時行政長官，。如中國國家主席習近平同意，臨時行政長官將於2020年3月，即是兩會會議舉行的月份就任，完成林鄭月娥餘下任期至2022年。《香港01》已就事件向特首辦查詢，特首辦尚未回覆。<br />\n創新及科技局長楊偉雄今早（23日）出席商台節目《在晴朗的一天出發》時被問及相關報道，楊偉雄稱現時換特首仍然只是傳言，不作評論，自己作為香港政府的官員，會繼續服務。<br />\n報道稱，熱門人選包括香港金融管理局前總裁陳德霖和前政務司司長唐英年；現任財政司司長陳茂波和...<a href=\"https://headline.klwpc.com/share.php?a=headlinewwd&amp;id=124168\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadline.klwpc.com%2Fshare.php%3Fa%3Dheadlinewwd%26id%3D124168&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltndT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=11309a8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://headline.klwpc.com/share.php?a=headlinewwd&amp;id=124168</a>"},{"pid":"7e0fcfaf9b44d557ec475c7ba0d801216af33a06","tid":1670337,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:20:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">一、誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltndT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=e80e2425\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltndT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=7ce6d85d\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltndT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=4debf754\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Fa